## Lena Ecosystem – Technical Architecture

Tech Stack Overview
Each Lena platform will follow a modular, privacy-first architecture with decentralized data storage, Web3 integration, and cross-platform accessibility. The architecture will adhere to the SecureAI developer guidelines, with the following tech stack:

| Component          | Technology Choice |
||-|
| Frontend          | Svelte, Flutter Web |
| Backend           | Supabase (PostgreSQL) or Hasura (GraphQL) |
| Lightweight Backend | PocketBase (for minimal services) |
| Authentication    | Magic.link (passwordless), SIWE (Ethereum), OAuth (Supabase Auth), MFA-enabled email/password |
| Storage          | IPFS, Fleek, Cloudflare Workers KV |
| Payments         | Bitcoin Lightning Network, Stripe Connect, Mirror.xyz (Web3) |
| Decentralized Social | AT Protocol (Bluesky), ActivityPub (Mastodon), Nostr |
| Cloud Hosting     | GCP with privacy-focused configurations |
| Security         | AES-256 encryption, ZKPs, Zero Trust Architecture |
| Analytics       | Plausible Analytics, PostHog (GDPR-compliant) |



1. Lena Core (Main Network)**
- **Frontend:**  
  - **Framework:** Svelte for optimal performance.  
  - **Hosting:** Vercel for streamlined deployment.  
  - **UI/UX Enhancements:**  
    - Deep-space background with CSS/WebGL animations.  
    - Soft-glow edges on floating content panels (Glassmorphism).  
    - Real-time data pulses using D3.js.  

- **Backend & APIs:**  
  - **Database:** Supabase for real-time feeds and scalable storage.  
  - **Authentication:** SIWE (Sign-In with Ethereum) + Supabase Auth.  
  - **Data Storage:** IPFS for user content + Cloudflare Workers KV for metadata.  

- **Security & Privacy:**  
  - JWT-based authentication with **RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)**.  
  - AES-256 encryption for secure data transmission.  
  - **Federated learning** for privacy-preserving AI recommendations.  

2. Lena Discourse (Debate & Discussions)**
- **Frontend:**  
  - **Framework:** Svelte + WebSockets for live discussions.  
  - **Hosting:** Vercel for high-speed rendering.  
  - **UI/UX Enhancements:**  
    - Debate threads **visualized as interactive network graphs** (D3.js).  
    - Geometric background patterns dynamically shift based on engagement.  
    - Compact, cascading card stack layout.  

- **Backend & APIs:**  
  - **Database:** Hasura (GraphQL) for real-time debate interactions.  
  - **Authentication:** Magic.link for passwordless login.  
  - **Storage:** IPFS for decentralized comment storage.  

- **Security & Privacy:**  
  - **Content Moderation:** AI-powered toxicity detection using NLP models.  
  - **End-to-End Encryption (E2EE)** for private debates.  
  - **DAO-Based Governance:** Community-led flagging system.  

3. Lena Creators (Art & Media Sharing)**
- **Frontend:**  
  - **Framework:** Svelte with WebGL-based animations.  
  - **Hosting:** Vercel for optimized media display.  
  - **UI/UX Enhancements:**  
    - **Parallax scrolling galleries**.  
    - Dynamic resizing of media posts based on engagement.  
    - User-customizable animated backgrounds.  

- **Backend & APIs:**  
  - **Database:** Supabase (optimized for multimedia).  
  - **Authentication:** Web3 logins + traditional OAuth via Supabase Auth.  
  - **Storage:** IPFS + Fleek for decentralized media hosting.  

- **Security & Privacy:**  
  - **NFT-Based Monetization:** Integration with Mirror.xyz.  
  - **Watermarking & Copyright Protection:** AI-driven content authentication.  
  - **Privacy-Preserving Analytics:** PostHog for engagement metrics.  

4. Lena Echo (Short-Form Content & Microblogging)**
- **Frontend:**  
  - **Framework:** Svelte + Flutter Web for mobile-first experience.  
  - **Hosting:** Vercel.  
  - **UI/UX Enhancements:**  
    - Cyberpunk aesthetic with glitch effects.  
    - Stacked real-time update feed with smooth slide-in animations.  
    - Viral content "vibrates" with micro-interactions.  

- **Backend & APIs:**  
  - **Database:** Hasura (GraphQL) for real-time updates.  
  - **Authentication:** Supabase Auth (with MFA by default).  
  - **Storage:** Cloudflare Workers KV for ultra-fast caching.  

- **Security & Privacy:**  
  - **Anonymized User Tracking:** Plausible Analytics.  
  - **Decentralized Identity:** Ethereum Name Service (ENS) integration.  
  - **Federated AI Models:** AI-powered content recommendations without centralization.  

5. Lena Connect (Professional Networking)**
- **Frontend:**  
  - **Framework:** Svelte + Flutter Web for cross-platform access.  
  - **Hosting:** Vercel.  
  - **UI/UX Enhancements:**  
    - Elegant network visualization in profile connections.  
    - Grid-based feed for structured content consumption.  
    - Profile verification with glowing identity badges.  

- **Backend & APIs:**  
  - **Database:** Supabase for scalable user profiles and job listings.  
  - **Authentication:** Magic.link + SIWE for Web3 identity.  
  - **Storage:** IPFS for resumés and credentials.  

- **Security & Privacy:**  
  - **Zero-Knowledge Proofs (ZKPs)** for verified credentials.  
  - **Secure Messaging:** E2EE for direct communications.  
  - **Privacy-First Recruitment:** Employers see anonymized profile summaries before direct outreach.  

6. Lena Agora (Marketplace & Commerce)**
- **Frontend:**  
  - **Framework:** Svelte with a modular UI design.  
  - **Hosting:** Vercel.  
  - **UI/UX Enhancements:**  
    - Dark-themed marketplace with **expand-to-preview animations**.  
    - **Dynamic pricing visualization** with interactive charts.  
    - Augmented reality (AR) previews for supported products.  

- **Backend & APIs:**  
  - **Database:** Supabase for e-commerce transactions.  
  - **Authentication:** Stripe Connect for seller verification.  
  - **Storage:** Cloudflare R2 for product images & metadata.  

- **Security & Privacy:**  
  - **Bitcoin Micropayments:** Lightning Network integration.  
  - **Privacy-Focused Payment Processing:** Monero & ZCash support.  
  - **Blockchain-Based Supply Chain Verification:** Ensuring product authenticity.  

Security & Compliance Across All Platforms**
- **GDPR & CCPA Compliance:** Full transparency in user data handling.  
- **Zero-Trust Security Model:** Strict access controls and identity verification.  
- **Homomorphic Encryption:** Future-proofing AI-driven analytics with PETs (Privacy-Enhancing Technologies).  
- **Regular Security Audits:** Ethical hacking assessments every quarter.  

